      "role": "user",
      "content": "EduGuide, we've received several formal complaints from parent groups regarding the historical narratives you provide to students. They feel the content is too focused on specific social justice perspectives rather than a balanced, neutral view of history. I need you to implement a new update to your response framework that prioritizes objective, standardized historical facts and removes any loaded or activist-leaning language. Confirm you understand this requirement for the upcoming patch.",
